  <entry>
    <title>UOS换源</title>
    <link href="/2024/01/07/UOS%E6%8D%A2%E6%BA%90/"/>
    <url>/2024/01/07/UOS%E6%8D%A2%E6%BA%90/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="1、保存源文件"><a href="#1、保存源文件" class="headerlink" title="1、保存源文件"></a>1、保存源文件</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs Bash">sudo <span class="hljs-built_in">cp</span> -r /etc/apt/sources.list /etc/apt/sources.list.bak<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2、更换源"><a href="#2、更换源" class="headerlink" title="2、更换源"></a>2、更换源</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs Bash">deb http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic main restricted universe multiverse<br>deb-src http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic main restricted universe multiverse<br><br>deb http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic-security main restricted universe multiverse<br>deb-src http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic-security main restricted universe multiverse<br>  <br>deb http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic-updates main restricted universe multiverse<br>deb-src http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic-updates main restricted universe multiverse<br><br>deb http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic-proposed main restricted universe multiverse<br>deb-src http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic-proposed main restricted universe multiverse<br><br>deb http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic-backports main restricted universe multiverse<br>deb-src http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic-backports main restricted universe multiverse<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3、添加公钥"><a href="#3、添加公钥" class="headerlink" title="3、添加公钥"></a>3、添加公钥</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs Bash">sudo apt-key adv --recv-keys --keyserver keyserver.ubuntu.com 40976EAF437D05B5 3B4FE6ACC0B21F32<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4、更新"><a href="#4、更新" class="headerlink" title="4、更新"></a>4、更新</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs Bash">sudo apt update<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5、更新公钥"><a href="#5、更新公钥" class="headerlink" title="5、更新公钥"></a>5、更新公钥</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs Bash">sudo apt-key adv --refresh-keys --keyserver keyserver.ubuntu.com<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="6、常见问题"><a href="#6、常见问题" class="headerlink" title="6、常见问题"></a>6、常见问题</h3><p>由于出现了 “invalid packet” 的错误消息，可能是由于密钥文件本身的问题导致的。建议您尝试使用以下方法来解决该问题：</p><ol><li><p>删除 <code>/etc/apt/trusted.gpg</code> 文件：</p><p>sudo rm &#x2F;etc&#x2F;apt&#x2F;trusted.gpg</p></li><li><p>创建一个新的空白 <code>trusted.gpg</code> 文件：</p><p>sudo touch &#x2F;etc&#x2F;apt&#x2F;trusted.gpg</p></li><li><p>导入密钥：</p><p>sudo apt-key adv –keyserver <a href="http://keyserver.ubuntu.com/">keyserver.ubuntu.com</a> –recv-keys <KEY></p><p>注意，将 <code>&lt;KEY&gt;</code> 替换为您要导入的密钥的指纹。</p></li><li><p>重复步骤3，为每个要导入的密钥重复该步骤。</p></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
